Distribution. Western Atlantic—USA (Florida), Gulf of Mexico, Panama , Antilles, Colombia , Guianas, and Brazil (Pará, Maranhão , Ceará , Rio Grande do Norte , Paraíba , Alagoas , Pernambuco , Sergipe , Rio de Janeiro , São Paulo , Santa Catarina). Eastern Atlantic—Cape Verde to Angola ( Rathbun 1901 , 1930 ; Holthuis 1959 ; Fausto-Filho 1966; Coelho & Ramos 1972 ; Powers 1977 ; Lemaitre 1981 ; Abele & Kim 1986 ;
